{
  "id": "RAW_f79f10",
  "title": "如何成为顶尖的 AI 产品经理",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNjkzNDMzMA==&mid=2247483661&idx=1&sn=1aad9ce11c160a436eafc16fab84c32b&subscene=0",
  "date": "2025-04-05 16:26:00",
  "author": "yikai",
  "siteName": "yikai 的摸鱼笔记",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:16px 0;box-shadow:0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);max-width:100%;color:#333333;letter-spacing:0.2px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'PingFang SC', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">播客介绍与嘉宾背景</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">yikai</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">欢迎来到跨国串门计划，为您带来全球领先的AI、财经、健康和科技领域播客精华。本期节目邀请到AI产品管理领域的重量级嘉宾Aman Khan，现任Arise AI产品总监，曾在Spotify、Cruise、Zipline和Apple等顶尖科技公司担任要职，拥有丰富的AI产品实战经验。他强调自己是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">独立产出者</span></span><span leaf=\"\">(Independent Contributor)。本期将深入探讨如何进入AI产品管理领域、如何成为优秀的AI产品经理、三类AI产品经理（</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI平台产品经理</span></span><span leaf=\"\">、</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI应用产品经理</span></span><span leaf=\"\">、</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI赋能型产品经理</span></span><span leaf=\"\">）的见解、AI PM常用提效工具（如</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor</span></span><span leaf=\"\">、</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Replit</span></span><span leaf=\"\">、</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">V0</span></span><span leaf=\"\">），以及给转型者的建议。Aman还分享了作为</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">独立贡献型产品经理</span></span><span leaf=\"\">的成长经验，强调保持积极能量、理解用户需求和持续探索的重要性。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan是Arise AI的产品总监，在AI产品领域经验丰富，曾在Spotify负责机器学习平台，并在Cruise、Zipline和Apple任职。他被广泛认为是顶尖的</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">独立贡献型产品经理</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。今天我们重点讨论：如何进入AI领域，以及如何成为优秀的AI产品经理。我们会分析不同类型AI PM的特点，探讨独立贡献型产品经理的路径，以及Aman的职业发展经验。当前产品领域最火的两个趋势是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI技术</span></span><span leaf=\"\">和</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">独立贡献者</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，Aman同时具备这两个特质。很多PM在思考如何切入AI赛道，同时行业趋势也更看重独立贡献者，资深技术专家增多，管理岗缩减。Aman长期专注AI并保持独立贡献者定位，因此本次对话将围绕AI入行、AI PM进阶及非AI领域IC如何突围展开。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个安排很到位。产品与AI的结合是当下最热门的话题，期待深入探讨并分享我的心得。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\"></section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于想转型做AI产品经理的朋友，是什么帮助你完成这个转型的？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">现在涉足AI产品管理领域其实比以前更容易了。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\">YouTube上有很多高质量教学视频，几小时就能教你开发一个应用，这在一年前是难以想象的。以前进入大厂做AI产品需要过硬的机器学习背景，要真正懂AI开发。 产品经理的核心是连接设计、工程、商务、运营、销售等团队，将产品落地并产生影响，关键在于</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">替用户说话</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，解决他们的问题。我认为AI产品经理可分三类：&nbsp;</span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">1.</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI平台产品经理</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：为AI工程师打造工具平台。我现在在Arise AI做的就是AI可观测性和效果评估平台，帮助AI工程师理解技术落地效果，向管理层证明AI应用达到设计目标。我们从机器学习（排序、回归、分类）起步，现在扩展到所有AI技术，近期重点是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">大语言模型(LLM)</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。基于LLM的开发仍处于初级阶段，开发和测试工具尚不完善。&nbsp;</span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">2.</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI应用产品经理</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：工作重心完全放在AI原生产品上，典型如</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">ChatGPT</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，还有Ryzon智能助手、</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Notebook LM</span></span><span leaf=\"\">笔记应用等。这类产品的核心体验基于底层模型，PM的任务是将前沿AI技术整合应用，让企业和用户受益。</span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">3.</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI赋能型产品经理</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：这类PM的工作是利用AI技术优化产品经理工作的各个环节。你可能不需从头搭建模型，但可以基于现有LLM或其他模型，构建最佳用户体验。</span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">随着AI普及，它可能像数据库一样成为SaaS应用的标配。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">未来大多数PM可能都会转型为此类AI产品经理，要么为其他PM开发工具，要么帮企业部署AI解决方案，或者围绕现有模型（如transformer或GPT）构建方案，用AI替代部分人工工作。</span>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI产品经理的提效工具</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">你在产品管理日常中都用哪些提效工具？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">我常用</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor</span></span><span leaf=\"\">和</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Replit</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，它们能让我快速构建原型，理解各种可能性。这使得产品经理可以直接带着可交互的原型去开会，虽然不是最终成品，但足以演示核心功能。 推荐Vercel推出的</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">V0</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，输入文字描述即可生成着陆页，通过迭代甚至能输出可用的UI界面，辅助设计团队制作初稿。 在界面设计、Logo制作或用视觉元素讲故事时，可以使用</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Midjourney</span></span><span leaf=\"\">和</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">DALL·E</span></span><span leaf=\"\">这类AI绘画工具，关键在于写好提示词。对于重视用户体验的公司，可视化工具尤其有用。 3D建模领域也出现了很多新工具，对硬件产品开发流程有很大帮助。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">现在有了AI技术，产品经理完全可以带着初步方案（原型）去开会，而不是仅凭产品需求文档(PRD)，这样起点更清晰。</span>\n     </section>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如何转型成为AI产品经理</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于想转型AI PM的朋友，你会建议他们掌握哪些技能？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">我也是转行过来的（本科机械工程），计算机和AI知识大多是自学的。无论是做AI基建PM还是AI产品技术PM，</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心都是真正关心终端用户，对解决问题本身充满热情</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。当你热爱解决某个问题时，自然会想办法用新技术突破瓶颈。 我专注于帮助AI工程师和数据科学家解决看似不复杂但深入后发现很复杂的问题（如模型监控面板），这推动了技术进步。AI产品经理也是如此，设计最佳客户体验，解决他们的问题。深入研究理想解决方案，自然会找到方法。例如优化客服电话体验，减少摩擦，AI实时对话（如ChatGPT Plus的语音交互）就是一种实现方式。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">关键在于保持好奇心，驱动你去尝试各种工具。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">这能让你看清动力来源，找到实现理想体验的工具。 要申请AI PM职位，需考虑两方面：掌握哪些核心技能？如何在竞争中脱颖而出？ 1.</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心知识</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：理解AI技术的运作原理和适用边界。 2.</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">实践应用</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：通过实际使用工具探索其可能性，并将技术应用于你关心的问题或行业。 3.</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">作品集</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：将开发过的产品（哪怕是原型）整理成作品集。这能向招聘经理展示你的能力、热情和思考方式，可能让你跳过前几轮筛选。面试主要考察能力、热情和合作性，作品集能提前回答前两个问题。</span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">我的建议：构建技能组合，跟随好奇心学习，整理成果为作品集。</span>\n     </section>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">这建议很实用。用AI做出产品（现在比以前容易多了），会让你在求职中更有优势。工具包括代码工具</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">V0</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Replit</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，以及设计工具</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Midjourney</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">DALL·E</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在进入AI PM领域确实比以前容易。以前需要扎实的机器学习基础，懂模型、训练数据、部署等。现在YouTube上有很多快速开发应用的教程（如Greg Eisenberg的演示）。 科技趋势是让事情变简单。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">作为产品经理，保持好奇心至关重要，让你能第一时间发现新技术并思考如何应用，成为团队的技术风向标。</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;max-width: 100%; background: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 2px; \\n                  padding: 16px 0; box-shadow: 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); \\n                  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'PingFang SC', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\\n                  color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.2px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 11px; padding-right: 10px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">保持对行业的热忱和探索欲是PM必备素质。</span>\n     </section>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI时代产品经理的核心价值</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">有人猜测AI工具可能取代PM。但我认为，AI擅长执行构建，而PM的核心价值在于：发现市场机会和用户痛点（</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">知道该做什么</span></span><span leaf=\"\">）、清晰传达需求给AI（</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">如何表达</span></span><span leaf=\"\">）、以及判断什么是好产品（</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">产品品味</span></span><span leaf=\"\">）。你觉得PM在AI时代是否更重要了？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">完全认同。高管们焦虑于\"必须搞AI\"，但常沿用老路。AI PM需要成为公司里最懂这些工具的人，连接技术和需求，判断\"该做什么\"。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">这种连接技术和需求的桥梁角色现在至关重要，让AI PM成为公司里最具影响力的职位之一。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">AI工具能帮助PM将影响力最大化，通过原型与各团队沟通，明确方向。</span>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如何成为顶尖的AI产品经理</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">普通AI PM和顶尖5%的大牛，最大区别在哪？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">ChatGPT发布时令人惊艳，但技术进步飞快，现在的模型远超当时。我们服务的顶尖客户（如Spotify, Instacart）在AI浪潮初期，不约而同地基于自有数据开发自己的类ChatGPT系统，特别是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于知识库的企业聊天机器人</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。但实际使用率可能并不理想。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">顶尖AI PM的关键在于走差异化路线，而不是简单复制现有成功模式（如聊天机器人界面）。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">要思考这是否是真正需要解决的核心问题，AI的交互方式可能完全不同。它可以优化人工环节，让工作更省心。例如，我们内部尝试自动化数据分析，设计的AI交互界面就与聊天机器人不同。许多前沿AI应用不一定是聊天机器人形态。关键问题是：</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">什么样的交互方式最合适？</span></span><span leaf=\"\">如果团队开发的东西与基础模型产品（如ChatGPT）太像，这可能是个警示信号，表明创新不足。应该关注更有</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">创新性的方向</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。 最近大家开始集中讨论</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI智能体(AI Agents)</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。但很多人只强调技术方案(\"用AI智能体做XX\")，没说清楚要解决的具体问题。公司是否需要自研AI代理？还是让基础模型公司整合代理层更好？</span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">PM的价值在于将这些技术无缝整合进产品，让用户几乎察觉不到。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">我们不太可能自建顶尖研究团队，但可以利用现有技术，找到最适合业务场景的用法。 在寻找优质AI应用创意方面： 1.</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">明确核心评估指标</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：目前尚无衡量AI原型开发效果的统一指标。需要思考如何评估AI项目的实际业务影响。 2.</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">鼓励尝试（如黑客松）</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：让员工亲自上手，打破技术壁垒，培养直觉。设定问题，用AI尝试解决，看哪些可行，哪些不合适（如AI在需要精确答案时可能不适用）。我们内部黑客松尝试用AI做Slack机器人自动分派求助，发现比预期复杂得多。 3.</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">死磕用户感受细节</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：研究成功的AI产品如何运作。思考用户在哪些环节被AI惊艳到。例如，</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Betty Crocker蛋糕粉</span></span><span leaf=\"\">案例表明，完全自动化未必是最好的，用户希望保留一些</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">控制感</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。Waymo自动驾驶允许乘客调空调音乐，Blue Apron提供烹饪参与感。</span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">成功的AI产品往往不是完全自动化，而是适当给用户控制权，降低创作或操作难度，让过程更轻松。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">顶尖AI PM还需要具备</span>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">“边走路边嚼口香糖”的多任务处理能力</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;max-width: 100%; background: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 2px; \\n                  padding: 16px 0; box-shadow: 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); \\n                  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'PingFang SC', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\\n                  color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.2px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 11px; padding-right: 10px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">（引用Kevin Yin的观点）</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">核心是解决客户问题，而非交付AI本身。但在实际工作中，需要平衡业务KPI和探索性工作（原型设计、试用工具、组织黑客松、案例分析）。</span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">必须学会一心二用：持续创造客户价值，同时给自己留出探索和试错的空间。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">AI技术快速迭代，失败是常态，要适应并从中学习。不要放弃</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">北极星目标</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，要为AI在组织内的应用推广留出空间。 AI领域炒作很多，PM的核心能力是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">准确判断什么产品值得做</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。梳理市场动向，真正解决用户痛点，才能体现价值。这是最具挑战但也最能创造影响力的环节。</span>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如何成为优秀的独立贡献者(IC) PM</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">你选择保持IC身份，而非走向管理岗。要长期保持优秀IC水准，关键习惯、思维和经验是什么？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心在于</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">个人驱动力</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，我着迷于解决客户的实际问题，需要深挖细节。ICPM面临的挑战是如何在信息过载、节奏快、干扰多（会议、救火）的环境下完成工作。我认为关键靠三点： 1.</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">保持积极能量状态</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：当你精神饱满时，很多矛盾更容易化解。这种能量能感染他人，拉近距离，使沟通更顺畅。遇到难题或卡壳时（产品瓶颈），要接受状态，但更要</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">亲自上阵解决问题</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。例如，我曾主动学习销售技巧，联系潜在客户，向团队展示解决问题的决心和行动力，即便在忙于日常工作时也要投入时间探索新方向。这种\"既当教练又当队员\"的做法在团队迷茫时尤其有效。每个人展现能量的方式不同（投入、热情、关心同事、带动气氛），但关键是让大家感受到你的</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">全身心投入</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，带动气氛而非让场子冷下来。Lyft早期团队喊\"使命必达\"口号也是一个例子，小举动能塑造团队文化和信念。会议室的氛围掌握在PM手中，你的能量场能左右团队士气。 2.</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">区分“等待”与“游荡”(Wandering vs. Waiting)</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：高管常倾向于\"等等看\"，尤其在AI领域（等下一代模型）。有时等待是明智的，但不能停止探索。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">PM应主动去“游荡”，探索新方向，为团队探路。</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">当产品方向不明时，PM会感到迷茫，像在黑暗中摸索。优秀的AI PM需要像开拓者，习惯待在</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">不确定性</span></span><span leaf=\"\">中，不断摸索尝试，直到感觉产品在引导你前进。不用每个决定都十拿九稳，边走边看。 3.</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">利用工具捕捉关键信号</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：AI可以作为</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">信号增强器</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，在海量信息中捕捉零散但重要的信号。例如，使用</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gong</span></span><span leaf=\"\">分析客户（工程师）需求，将记录输入大模型提炼常见问题。利用AI扩展能力边界，抓住关键信息。 最后，</span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">放轻松，享受过程</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">这是我从一位多次创业上市的董事会成员那里得到的建议。让热情驱动你，持续学习，保持好奇，为客户打磨产品。当你热爱所做之事，过程会充满乐趣，迭代速度也会加快。人生是探索，享受其中的曲折。</span>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个\"享受过程\"的观点我非常认同，我桌上就贴着写有这四个字的便利贴。即使面对压力和恐惧，寻找乐趣也能改变局面。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">快问快答</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">平时最爱推荐哪两三本书？</span><speaker name=\"Lenny Rachitsky\">\n       <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;max-width: 100%; background: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 2px; \\n                  padding: 16px 0; box-shadow: 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); \\n                  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'PingFang SC', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\\n                  color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.2px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 11px; padding-right: 10px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;speaker&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Lenny Rachitsky&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">最近有什么上头的影视作品推荐吗？</span>\n      </speaker></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. &nbsp;比尔·布莱森的</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">《万物简史》</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：以有趣的方式讲述科学史和科学家故事，让人重新思考宇宙尺度和人类存在的短暂，尤其在AI时代。 2. &nbsp;[书名未明确说出，但提到一个练习] 一本关于人生意义的书：其中一个练习是分别写下\"工作对你意味着什么\"和\"生命的意义是什么\"，然后看两者共通之处。</span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">这个练习能帮人在职业迷茫时找到动力和方向。</span>\n     </section><speaker name=\"Lenny Rachitsky\">\n      <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n     </speaker>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">Netflix的纪录片</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">《环法自行车赛：逆风飞驰》(Tour de France: Unchained)</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。制作团队与《F1：极速争胜》相同。职业自行车赛的水平和运动员的故事非常打动人。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近有没有让你欲罢不能的新产品？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI原型工具如</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Replit</span></span><span leaf=\"\">和</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">V0</span></span><span leaf=\"\">很出色。最近收获最大的是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">WebSIM</span></span><span leaf=\"\">（可能是指某个模拟或原型工具，具体名称可能需核实），它能创造有趣的、甚至天马行空的原型。 另外，一个用</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">苹果回收材料</span></span><span leaf=\"\">制作的记事本，品牌是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">Apeel</span></span><span leaf=\"\">(A-P-E-E-L)。翻开时有淡淡苹果香气，这种感官体验让我更喜欢使用它。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">有没有特别受用的人生信条？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">引用乔布斯的话：</span></p>\n     <section style=\"border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;padding:10px 12px;margin:8px 0;border-left:3px solid #4A6FA5;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">“你的时间有限，所以不要浪费时间去过别人的生活。”</span>\n     </section><span leaf=\"\">这句话提醒我要想清楚自己想要什么样的人生，而不是活在社会压力或他人期望中。要反复问自己：你想要过怎样的生活？并据此做决定。</span>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">你的名字在网上搜出来常是同名的板球运动员，对此你怎么看？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">（开玩笑）爸妈取名时没考虑SEO。现在想被搜到很难。不过未来可能更依赖LLM而非传统搜索，这也许给了我重新成为训练数据一部分的机会。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 0 20px 15px 20px;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"margin:10px 0 12px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.4px;font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语与联系方式</span></h1>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">非常感谢Aman的分享，内容对想进入AI、成为优秀AI PM或走IC路线的人都很有帮助。听众可以通过什么方式联系你？有什么需要听众帮助的吗？</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">最方便的渠道是</span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgba(251, 211, 141, 0.4);border-radius:3px;padding:2px 5px;font-weight:500;\"><span leaf=\"\">LinkedIn</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。我会回复所有消息，除非是纯粹的推销。借鉴John Doerr的做法：如果你在消息中分享三部对你影响最大的书、电影或播客，我会回复我的私人推荐清单。期待大家的分享。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lenny Rachitsky</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">再次感谢Aman！</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding: 14px 20px 5px 20px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;display: flex;align-items: center;\">\n     <span style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Khan</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 11px;padding-right: 10px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;font-weight: 400;color: #2D3748;\"><span leaf=\"\">谢谢Lenny，对谈非常愉快。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Aman Khan 分享了成为顶尖 AI 产品经理的实战策略，强调好奇心、用户价值、持续探索和差异化竞争。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Aman Khan 分享了成为顶尖 AI 产品经理的实战策略，强调好奇心、用户价值、持续探索和差异化竞争。",
  "summary": "Aman Khan 在播客中分享了他作为 Arise AI 产品总监，以及在 Spotify、Cruise、Zipline 和 Apple 等公司积累的顶尖 AI 产品经理实战经验。他将 AI 产品经理分为三类：AI 平台产品经理、AI 应用产品经理和 AI 赋能型产品经理，并推荐了 Cursor、Replit 和 V0 等提效工具。他强调了转型 AI PM 需要掌握的核心技能，包括理解 AI 技术原理、实践应用和作品集展示。Aman 认为，AI 时代 PM 的核心价值在于发现市场机会和用户痛点，并清晰传达需求。他建议顶尖 AI PM 要走差异化路线，关注用户感受细节，并具备多任务处理能力。他还分享了作为独立贡献者 (IC) PM 的经验，强调保持积极能量、区分 \"等待\" 与 \"游荡\"、以及利用工具捕捉关键信号。AI 产品经理在 AI 时代至关重要，他们连接技术与需求，驱动创新。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI PM 的核心是连接技术与用户价值",
      "explanation": "AI PM 应成为公司里最懂 AI 工具的人，弥合技术与用户需求的鸿沟，确保 AI 应用真正解决实际问题，创造价值。"
    },
    {
      "point": "顶尖 AI PM 需走差异化路线，关注用户感受细节",
      "explanation": "避免简单复制现有模式，深入研究用户需求，设计最合适的交互方式，适当给予用户控制权，提升产品体验。"
    },
    {
